        <h2>About Brat Music: Your Personal Music Upload Platform</h2>

        <p><strong>Brat Music</strong> is a web-based application inspired by the sleek design and user-friendly interface of Spotify, allowing users to upload, manage, and listen to their personal music collections. Designed for music lovers, Brat Music provides a platform for individuals to showcase their favorite tracks while fostering a sense of community through shared musical experiences.</p>

        <h3>How It Works</h3>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>User-Friendly Interface:</strong> Brat Music features a modern and intuitive layout, making it easy for users to navigate through their music library. The dark theme, reminiscent of Spotify, provides an immersive listening experience.</li>
            <li><strong>Music Uploads:</strong> Users can effortlessly upload their music by filling out a simple form that requires:
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Music Name:</strong> The title of the track.</li>
                    <li><strong>MP3 File:</strong> A straightforward file upload for the music file (MP3 format).</li>
                    <li><strong>Album Cover:</strong> An optional image upload for the album cover, allowing users to personalize their tracks.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Dynamic Music Library:</strong> After uploading, users can see their tracks displayed in a personal hits section, showcasing album covers and song titles.</li>
            <li><strong>Delete Functionality:</strong> Users have the ability to manage their library by deleting songs they no longer wish to keep, ensuring a clutter-free experience.</li>
            <li><strong>Responsive Design:</strong> The platform is fully responsive, allowing users to access their music collection on various devices, including smartphones, tablets, and desktops.</li>
            <li><strong>Community Features:</strong> Plans for future development include user accounts, sharing options, and playlists, fostering a vibrant community of music enthusiasts.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Technology Stack</h3>
        <p>Brat Music is built using:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> HTML, CSS, and JavaScript for a seamless user experience.</li>
            <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js and Express for handling server-side logic and file uploads.</li>
            <li><strong>Database:</strong> A database (like MongoDB or MySQL) to store user data and music metadata.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Conclusion</h3>
        <p>With Brat Music, users can turn their music aspirations into reality, creating a personal music library where they can upload, manage, and enjoy their favorite tracks. Join us on this musical journey, and unleash your creativity!</p>
